  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Extreme compression turns the drum circle into a pumping, breathing entity. Threshold at -24dB with ratio 8:1 and fast attack — every hit ducks the others. The compressor IS the instrument.",
