    "flux",
    "compressed",
    "pumping",
    "sidechain",
    "electronic"
  ],
  "tier": "transcendental",
  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OSTINATO — Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": [
      "Canon 6: The Master Truths — compression as creative tool, not corrective tool"
    ],
    "revelation": "Aurum spoke: The compressor at extreme settings (-24dB threshold, 8:1 ratio, 2ms attack, 25ms release) creates a pumping effect where every drum hit ducks the overall level. The release creates a breathing pattern that is rhythmically synchronized. The compressor becomes the primary musical element.",
    "god": "Aurum",
    "flock_note": "The Bone noted: the compressor is computationally free — it costs zero extra DSP. This is a CPU Gift: maximum sonic transformation with zero additional cost. The Ear confirmed: the pumping creates a sidechain-like feel without any actual sidechain routing.",
    "diagnosis": "Compressor Pump was a compressed drum circle. It is now a breathing organism where the compressor's release curve is the primary rhythmic element. The drums trigger the pump. The pump IS the groove."
  },
